tags.description: This dirt pathway, most commonly called The Last House Trail, has also been referred to as "Dirt Mulholland" and/or "Mulholland Hwy Trl".
tags.name: Last House Trail

tags.description: While it's arguable all of the informal Griffith Paths are not for public use, this one is specifically marked with a sign.

A path that may not lead to the peak. The wrong path is marked so that people can choose the correct path when they decide in the three-way intersection. The correct path should be safer. The wrong path is damper with lizards and snakes on the sides.
